004package mkt;
005
006import java.util.ArrayList;
007import kut.Js;
008import kut.Arr;
009
010/** Result of 'Strategy.xxxSimple2'. */
011public class StSimple2Rs {
012  /** Number of sales. */
013  public final int sales;
014  /** Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with closes. */
015  public final double assets;
016  /** Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with prices. */
017  public final double accs;
018  /** Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with references. */
019  public final double rfAssets;
020  /** Profits ratio average. Portfolio evaluated with closes. */
021  public final double profits;
022  /** Profits ratio average. Portfolio evaluated with references. */
023  public final double rfProfits;
024
025  /**
026   * Constructor.
027   * @param sales Number of sales.
028   * @param assets Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with closes.
029   * @param accs Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with prices.
030   * @param rfAssets Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with references.
031   * @param profits Profits ratio average. Portfolio evaluated with closes.
032   * @param rfProfits Profits ratio average. Portfolio evaluated with references.
033   */
034  public StSimple2Rs (
035    int sales, double assets, double accs, double rfAssets,
036    double profits, double rfProfits
037  ) {
038    this.sales = sales;
039    this.assets = assets;
040    this.accs = accs;
041    this.rfAssets = rfAssets;
042    this.profits = profits;
043    this.rfProfits = rfProfits;
044  }
045
046  /**
047   * Returns object JSONized.
048   * @param o Ditto.
049   * @return Ditto.
050   */
051  public static String toJs (StSimple2Rs o) {
052    return Js.w(Arr.mk(
053      Js.w(o.sales),
054      Js.w(o.assets),
055      Js.w(o.accs),
056      Js.w(o.rfAssets),
057      Js.w(o.profits),
058      Js.w(o.rfProfits)
059    ));
060  }
061
062  /**
063   * Returns object from JSON.
064   * @param js JSON string.
065   * @return Ditto.
066   */
067  public static StSimple2Rs fromJs (String js) {
068    ArrayList<String> a = Js.ra(js);
069    return new StSimple2Rs(
070      (int)Js.rn(a.get(0)),
071      Js.rn(a.get(1)),
072      Js.rn(a.get(2)),
073      Js.rn(a.get(3)),
074      Js.rn(a.get(4)),
075      Js.rn(a.get(5))
076    );
077  }
078}
